author: Russell Brand
description:
Governments and billionaires are quietly funding geoengineering experiments to dim the sun, spraying particles into the atmosphere under the guise of “climate solutions.” Internal documents and emails reveal secret tests, PR strategies to hide projects from the public, and even Bill Gates’ backing. From military weather manipulation to cloud-brightening programs, these schemes expose a chilling reality: they lie about their intentions, claim it’s for our protection, and consolidate more control. The real question isn’t whether they can block out the sun—it’s why they don’t want us to know.

[UNPACKED]
